name: JJK1 - The Golden Maknae
description:
Inspired by recent BTS' Vogue and GQ photoshoot that goes down history, here is Jung Kook, the Golden Maknae of BTS. His look is another level. Blue silvery hair, piercings, Louis Vuitton x Virgil Abloh. It's really mesmerizing in every way.

This will come in a series.

Hand drawn and edited digitally.
1500 x 1500 px
